    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Males or females, between 18 and 75 years of age, inclusive

          -  Histologically confirmed NASH diagnosis

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Clinically significant acute or chronic liver disease

          -  Prior liver transplantation
      </textblock>
